  "texts": [
    "Along with EEG signals, participants were asked to report their emotions while watching music videos, using as the label for emotion recognition.",
    "After pre-processing (see Methods), EEG signals were fed to one-layer DH-SFNNs with different numbers of dendritic branches.",
    "We use DH-SFNNs to recognize three levels (low, medium and high) of valence and arousal which reflect emotion on the DEAP dataset (see Methods for more details).",
    "The accuracy curves during model training are provided in Fig. 7b, c.",
    "We find that DH-SFNNs show much better performance than vanilla SFNNs in both tasks."
  ],
